ratings.comment: This was the most boring class ever. Not only was it boring, they had a dumb "no electronics" rule. I didn't know we were in middle school. The TA's were basically only in class to serve as body guards and to tell people to not use electronics.  I wouldnt recommend this class to anyone, good thing my major isn't Social Work. Waste of time.

She was a terrible teacher. The class was very unorganized and the tests were easy, but terrible. She didn't make enough copies of the test for the final exam, so half the class had to wait an hour for her to come back. Don't take this class with her if you don't have to.
